pe=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Individuals</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Benjamin_Bloom\" title=\"Benjamin Bloom\">Benjamin Bloom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jerome_Bruner\" title=\"Jerome Bruner\">Jerome Bruner</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Rheta_DeVries\" title=\"Rheta DeVries\">Rheta DeVries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Caleb_Gattegno\" title=\"Caleb Gattegno\">Caleb Gattegno</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Constance_Kamii\" title=\"Constance Kamii\">Constance Kamii</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Maria_Montessori\" title=\"Maria Montessori\">Maria Montessori</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Jean_Piaget\" title=\"Jean Piaget\">Jean Piaget</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/William_Spady\" title=\"William Spady\">William Spady</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Marc_Tucker\" title=\"Marc Tucker\">Marc Tucker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Lev_Vygotsky\" title=\"Lev Vygotsky\">Lev Vygotsky</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Theories</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Active_learning\" title=\"Active learning\">Active learning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Block_scheduling\" title=\"Block scheduling\">Block scheduling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Cognitive_load\" title=\"Cognitive load\">Cognitive load</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Constructivism_(philosophy_of_education)\" title=\"Constructivism (philosophy of education)\">Constructivism</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Developmentally_appropriate_practice\" title=\"Developmentally appropriate practice\">Developmentally appropriate practice</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Discovery_learning\" title=\"Discovery learning\